.SH STANDARDS
Not in POSIX.1.
Present on the BSDs, Solaris, and many other systems.
.SH NOTES
Unlike some
.BR bindresvport ()
implementations,
the glibc implementation ignores any value that the caller supplies in
.IR sin\->sin_port .
